languages.text: "Где расцветают железные цветы Омниссии, там должно быть и страстным садовникам Его. Благодарю, что оказали данной единице честь служить грозному духу флагмана фон Валанциус и Вашей Светлости".

"Where the iron flowers of the Omnissiah bloom, there must also be His passionate gardeners. Thank you for honouring this unit by letting it serve the formidable spirit of the von Valancius dynasty's flagship and Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

languages.text: «Allá donde florecen las flores de hierro del Omnissiah deben también encontrarse Sus fieles jardineros. Gracias por honrar a esta unidad permitiéndole servir al formidable espíritu de la nave insignia de la dinastía von Valancius y a mi{mf|lord|lady}».
languages.original_text: "Where the iron flowers of the Omnissiah bloom, there must also be His passionate gardeners. Thank you for honouring this unit by letting it serve the formidable spirit of the von Valancius dynasty's flagship and Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

languages.text: 「万機神の鉄の花が咲くところには、神に仕える情熱的な庭師もいるに違いありません。フォン・ヴァランシウス王朝の旗艦の強大な精神と陛下に仕えることは、このユニットに名誉を与えてくれました。感謝を申し上げます」
languages.original_text: "Where the iron flowers of the Omnissiah bloom, there must also be His passionate gardeners. Thank you for honouring this unit by letting it serve the formidable spirit of the von Valancius dynasty's flagship and Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

languages.text: "Wo die Eisenblumen des Omnissiah blühen, dort müssen auch seine leidenschaftlichen Gärtner sein. Danke, dass Ihr dieser Einheit die große Ehre gewährt habt, dem formidablen Geist des Flaggschiffs der Dynastie von Valancius zu dienen — und Euch, Euer {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}."
languages.original_text: "Where the iron flowers of the Omnissiah bloom, there must also be His passionate gardeners. Thank you for honouring this unit by letting it serve the formidable spirit of the von Valancius dynasty's flagship and Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}."

languages.text: « Où que poussent les fleurs d'acier de l'Omnimessie, Ses zélés jardiniers doivent répondre présents. Merci d'avoir honoré cette unité en lui permettant de servir l'auguste esprit du vaisseau amiral des von Valancius, ainsi que Votre Seigneurie. »

languages.text: "Hermesih'in demir çiçeklerinin açtığı her yerde O'nun tutkulu bahçıvanları da bulunmalıdır. Bu birime, von Valancius hanedanlığının sancak gemisinin kudretli ruhuna ve {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri'ne hizmet etme onuru sunulduğu için ben teşekkür ederim."
